summary:
It’s okay guys...... just think.....
Tony is currently holding his 3 month old daughter. He’s missing those he lost and he...
body:
It’s okay guys…… just think…..

Tony is currently holding his 3 month old daughter. He’s missing those he lost and he thinks about Peter every day. But holding his girl to his chest, Pepper’s hand in his hair, he thinks maybe everything might be alright.

And it will. For a while.

We still have time. He still has time.

Steve goes back to return the Stones, for the sake of the universe.

The extra Pym Particles he palms when Bruce isn’t looking, though? Those are for the heart he has now and the heart he took into the ice; those are for the loves he’s known and held and lost and found, those—

Those are for the sake of his soul.

summary: The Golden Jaguar has been causing all sorts of problems for the kingdoms of Remnants by aiding the White Fang in major military...
question: The Golden Jaguar has been causing all sorts of problems for the kingdoms of Remnants by aiding the White Fang in major military ops (weather the Fang likes it or not) and the gods are well aware of this. So to even the odds, they bring the White Wolf (Bucky Barnes) to Remnant to help the kingdoms. (The Wakandans refer to Bucky as White Wolf at the end of Black Panther and Infinity War)
answer:
For a second there, I was going to go on a long thought process about how, technically, Gods couldn’t do this because of all the stuff about him not being dead or whatever.

And then I remembered that Gods of Remnant don’t give a fuck.

Even funnier, imagine that at the end of Infinity War, it wasn’t Thanos’ snap that turned Bucky into dust but Gods seeing what the Snap did and just stealthily kidnapping Barnes.

summary: Scott Lang introducing Luis to the Avengers for you, people. First picture after another long, long break. And I want to give a...
caption:
Scott Lang introducing Luis to the Avengers for you, people. First picture after another long, long break.

And I want to give a special dedication to @peterssquill for spreading the right message and welcoming people on board with this… not very obvious ship. Honestly… I’m surprised how many people are interested. Even canon ships from Ant-Man tend to be pushed away.

Anyway. I hope you like it. And I really want to post more, but my ideas look great in my head and then horribly on paper, so most of the pictures end up unfinished.


And btw… I’m sorry that Luis here looks like Michael Peña and RDJ’s child. The sketch captured his features quite nice and then the lineart decided to change it. Oh, well. Maybe next time I’ll got it right.



Other Marvel drawings that I’m not proud of, because they are old:

Iron Patriot <3

Sam and Riley

Ant-Man

Falcon & falcon

Female Winterfalcon

More like actors than the characters

Tiny Winterfalcon

Confused Winter Soldier at ComicCon

reblog.comment:
Scott Lang introducing Luis to the Avengers for you, people. First picture after another long, long break.

And I want to give a special dedication to @peterssquill for spreading the right message and welcoming people on board with this… not very obvious ship. Honestly… I’m surprised how many people are interested. Even canon ships from Ant-Man tend to be pushed away.

Anyway. I hope you like it. And I really want to post more, but my ideas look great in my head and then horribly on paper, so most of the pictures end up unfinished.


And btw… I’m sorry that Luis here looks like Michael Peña and RDJ’s child. The sketch captured his features quite nice and then the lineart decided to change it. Oh, well. Maybe next time I’ll got it right.



Other Marvel drawings that I’m not proud of, because they are old:

Sam and Riley

Ant-Man

Falcon & falcon

Female Winterfalcon

More like actors than the characters

summary: But MCU Spidey is the literal Canon! I mean, you are not one of those dumbasses who act like just because he doesn't have Uncle...
question: But MCU Spidey is the literal Canon! I mean, you are not one of those dumbasses who act like just because he doesn't have Uncle Ben shot he is not a Spider-man literally frok comic book pages.
answer:
Okay. That was kind of expected.

Look, as a person who likes and defends Jaune from all the hate he gets, I don’t want to spread hate on my own blog.

I respect your opinion on character and your right to love them as much as you want.

However, if I may, I would also like to ask you to respect my right to keep my own opinion regarding the particular version of Spider-Man. If you want, I could give you my reasons for not being his fan in private messages.
